"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Shilling is very necessary in the NFT space,  and if you’re doing it wrong, you’re causing more harm than good to your brand. Nobody wants to bet on a loser and every move you make on your socials can be seen by all. \\n\\nDON’T:\\n\\n\\\\-**Link and run**. If you don’t care enough to tell me a few lines about your project, why should I even bother to click? Take the time to make a post about the project, and save it in the Notes section of your phone for easy access. \\n\\n\\\\-**Spam.** Spamming and shilling are not the same thing. Don’t put links where links aren’t welcome, don’t drop your discord links the middle of irrelevant twitter threads, and don’t send out DMs to random people. \\n\\nDO:\\n\\n\\\\-**#create-shill.** Create a shill post that your community can use to promote your project. Include all the info they need to be successful, including how to snag their personal invite link from Discord. \\n\\n\\\\-**Build rapport**. Contributing to a community outside of just dropping your link in the shill zone can help boost your credibility, and ultimately, your community numbers. \\n\\n\\\\-**Engage.** Mention how your project relates to the community you’re shilling it in. Does it have similar utility or the same artist? Make it personal! \\n\\nDo you agree or disagree with these tips? What guidelines do you follow while shilling?\",\"timestamp\":1639949530,\"title\":\"A tale of two Shills...\"},\"digest\":\"ntocNC4u-nB1DteUC7tweTyxA4HG1UFU0YH7iwNszmc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9d4979cD1861a73c62a6DCAF698f7b812318cf29\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"63SHgK44TNoO-BYt8tjsbe30-XITiaJXa7-2X7FfyBY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ELcQIoxiMSxD7qXjwFzp1cuuaNCNYyDzTNqaVeTeS-s\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"JQCYwVeyCKcwdlHdDph0JJQev5GyMNelcWTXN25v8WDN1k1aDn6B9emBZKt4_QMOe_-XkWzSjkLK5U8glEMvCg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1b6fbae92631eb4952582c6ed50e00f